.    C                     Z-ADDH@QPC     D@QPC
.    C                     MOVE H@CRHZ    D@CRHZ
.    C                     MOVELH@CRME    D@CRME
.     * ADJ USER
.    C           D@CRME    IFEQ 'EDIUS'
.    C                     MOVEL'EDI  '   D@CRME
.    C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE '00'      @@NOBN
     C                     MOVE S@BIN     @@NOBN
     C                     MOVE D@DLVY    @@NONY
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     D@RQTY
      *
     C                     MOVELS@ORNO    @@ODRN
